name: Hatha Yoga
description: Hatha yoga focuses on foundational poses, alignment, and breathing techniques. It is an excellent choice for beginners and those looking to build a strong yoga foundation.

instructor.name: Rashika Khanna
instructor.bio: With a focus on breath and alignment, Rashika guides students to find strength, balance, and serenity through Hatha practice.

reviews.comment: I loved this class! Highly recommended for beginners.
Great class, but it could be a bit longer.

name: Vinyasa Flow
description: Vinyasa is a dynamic and flowing style of yoga that synchronizes breath with movement. It offers a cardiovascular workout while fostering mindfulness.

instructor.name: Amisha Sharma
instructor.bio: Amisha combines the art of dynamic movement with a deep understanding of yoga philosophy, creating a harmonious blend of mind and body in every class
